{
  "title": "Xtra Flaky Tunisian Lamb Tagine",
  "description": "A traditional Tunisian dish featuring tender lamb in a rich tomato sauce, with a unique yuzu cure and a flaky crust, perfect for special occasions.",
  "cuisine": "Tunisian",
  "diet": [
    "gluten-free",
